                                </svg>
                            </a>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="project-image right">
                        <img src="../../connect-4.png" alt="jungleMath" class="project-img">
                    </div>
                </article>



                <article class="project-card row">

                    <div class="project-content right">
                        <h2 class="project-1">Project</h2>
                        <h3 class="project-title-1"><a class="title-link" href="https://github.com/Yuvraj-Sandhu/Konnec-4" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">Konnec-4</a></h3>
                        <p class="project-desc-1 my-6">
                            Two-player Connect 4 game in Python, featuring object-oriented design with classes for game pieces and boards. 
                            Users can create custom instances. Robust exception handling ensures smooth gameplay by preventing crashes from invalid inputs.
                        </p>

                        <div class="project-subtitle-1 gap-8">
                            <h4 class="">Python</h4>
                        
                            <a href="https://github.com/Yuvraj-Sandhu/Konnec-4" target="_blank" class="project-link">
                                <svg 
