                </article>



                <article class="project-card my-16 lg:mx-80 row">
                    
                    <div class="project-content left">
                        <h2 class="project">Project</h2>
                        <h3 class="project-title"><a class="title-link" href="https://github.com/yuvraj-sandhu" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">Hospital Management System</a></h3>
                        <p class="project-desc my-6">
                            A Hospital Management System, built using Python and SQL database, it stores details of doctors, nurses, patients and manages appointments. 
                        </p>

                        <div class="project-subtitle gap-8">
                            <h4 class="">Python</h4>
                            <h4 class="">MySQL</h4>
        
                            <a href="https://github.com/yuvraj-sandhu" target="_blank" class="project-link">
                                <svg 
                                    xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" 
